-fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10837] updated the NU_LIB_DIRS delimiter for command line
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10821] fixed 
``main``
 not building due to errors later found in describe
gaetschwartz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10836] fixed 
``describe -d``
 for lazy records
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10795] added a 
``detailed``
 flag for 
``describe``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10728] made debug info lazy
WindSoilder fixed redirection bugs: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10835] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10816] 2
tertsdiepraam 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10488] implemented whoami using uutils
hudclark 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10829] extended pattern matching to support 
``null``
 literals
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10814] improved the 
``--flexible``
 flag on 
``from tsv``
 and 
``from csv``
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10828] added dataframe support for small int types
ludwig-austermann created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10824] readded the 
``--update``
 flag to 
``cp``
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10818] reverted "Bump regex from 1.9.6 to 1.10.2"
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10850] updated 
``str downcase``
 to use 
``to_lowercase``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10827] deprecated 
``glob --not``
 in favor of 
``glob --exclude``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10710] expand paths and split PATH in 
``std path add``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10277] synced 
``$env.config.filesize.metric``
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10807] finished removing the 
``profile``
 command and related data
CAD97 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10806] improved 
``registry value``
 return types
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10804] removed the registry clean_string hack
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10801] moved 
``ansi link``
 from extra to default feature
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10798] renamed 
``str size``
 to 
``str stats``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10797] updated Nushell version to v0.86 for release script
stfacc 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10796] fixed theming to not use white text in the default light theme
